## Libraries and Packages

### IEEE Library

The IEEE library contains standard packages used in digital design.

### Common Packages

#### STD_LOGIC_1164

Provides logic data types and operations.

vhdl
use IEEE.STD_LOGIC_1164.ALL;

#### NUMERIC_STD

Provides arithmetic operations on signed and unsigned numbers.

vhdl
use IEEE.NUMERIC_STD.ALL;


## Basic Data Types in VHDL

| Data Type        | Description                     |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------- |
| BIT              | Represents binary values 0 or 1 |
| BOOLEAN          | TRUE or FALSE                   |
| INTEGER          | Integer numbers                 |
| REAL             | Real numbers                    |
| STD_LOGIC        | Multi-valued logic type         |
| STD_LOGIC_VECTOR | Array of STD_LOGIC values       |
| SIGNED           | Signed binary number            |
| UNSIGNED         | Unsigned binary number          |



